<item>
            <title>[LU-12438] Use kernel_read/write instead of vfs_read/write  for PCC</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12438</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In the latest kernel (version 4.14), vfs_read/write are no long export kernel symbols any more.&#160; The merged PCC still calls the vfs_read/write functions. This rusults in the complile failure.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We should use kernel_read/write instead of vfs_read/write.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
